snippet: The European car market expanded 2.9 percent in October, topping 1.1 million units, but growth slowed in all major markets, according to figures released on Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: The European car market expanded 2.9 percent in October, topping 1.1 million units, but growth slowed in all major markets, according to figures released on Tuesday.

headline.main: European Car Market Grows, but Expansion Is Slowing
headline.print_headline: European Car Market Grows, but Expansion Is Slowing
